								Employee Self-Service website from the Internet. These are different
								than your employee number or Vulcan username and their associated passwords.
								Please refer to your VeSSO letter.

The Employee Self-Service Portal is intended only for Vulcan employees
								and approved agents.

									If you have problems or questions, please contact the Vulcan Materials
									Help Desk at 205.298.3700 or 800.615.4421.












