Home> Construction Materials> Products and Services> Recycled Materials




Recycled Materials Where practical, we recycle previously used concrete and asphalt paving materials. After careful inspection, these materials are re-crushed and sized to meet customer specifications for other uses. At times, the incoming material contains steel wire or rods that were used to support or reinforce the original structure. If steel is found, it is removed, sorted and shipped back to steel producers to be reused. For large-scale projects in some markets, we can provide on-site recycling, avoiding the cost and time it takes to transport materials to a recycling facility.




To find out more about local recycling requirements and speak to a sales representative, use our Facilities Map.

























